---
layout: layout-2-1-columns
---

<% content_for :breadcrumbs do %>
<%= partial(:'partial-breadcrumbs', :locals => { breadcrumb: [{ title: "Your businesses", url: "/index-10-december" }, { title: data.business.name, url: "/business"}, { title: "Business activites", url: "/business-activities"}] }) %>
<% end %>

<% content_for :column1 do %>

  <header class="page-header">
    <hgroup>
      <h1>Business activities</h1>
    </hgroup>
  </header>

  <form class="form" id="activities-form">
    <h3 class="heading-medium">Does the business run any of the following?</h3>

    <div class="form-group">

      <p>An airport, railway services, waterworks, real estate services or permanent sports and recreational grounds.</p>

      <div class="inline">
        <label for="activities-yes" class="block-label">
          <input type="radio" name="activities" id="activities-yes" value="yes" class="js-toggle" data-show="#activities-list">
          Yes
        </label>
        <label for="activities-no" class="block-label">
          <input type="radio" name="activities" id="activities-no" value="no" class="js-toggle" data-hide="#activities-list">
          No
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="form-group js-hidden" id="activities-list">
        <div class="form-group panel-indent">
          <p>Which of those does it operate?</p>

          <label for="ac1" class="form-label">
            <input type="checkbox" name="activites" id="ac1">
            Airport
          </label>

          <label for="ac2" class="form-label">
            <input type="checkbox" name="activites" id="ac2">
            Railway services
          </label>

          <label for="ac3" class="form-label">
            <input type="checkbox" name="activites" id="ac3">
            Waterworks
          </label>

          <label for="ac4" class="form-label">
            <input type="checkbox" name="activites" id="ac4">
            Real estate services
          </label>

          <label for="ac5" class="form-label">
            <input type="checkbox" name="activites" id="ac5">
            Permanent sports and recreational grounds
          </label>
        </div>

        <h3 class="heading-medium">Eligibility</h3>
        <p>As you run one of these businesses, your business isn't eligible for rural payments.</p>

        <p>You may still be able to claim if one of the following is true: </p>

        <ul class="list-bullet">
          <li>you have more than 36 ha of eligible land </li>
          <li>you got less than &euro;5,000 before deductions last year</li>
          <li>your SPS payment was at least 5% of your total non-agricultural receipts in the last financial year</li>
          <li>your total agricultural receipts are at least 15% of your total receipts in the last financial year</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="form-group">
      <a href="/business-january" class="button" id="set-activities">Continue</a>
    </div>

</form>


<% end %>

